  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To review the relationship of increased face mask usage arising from lockdown measures&#xD;
      instituted during the COVID-19 pandemic with dry eye symptoms on Chinese people, and make&#xD;
      recommendations for mitigating potential detrimental effects on dry eye symptoms.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
